# Clerk Authentication (https://clerk.com)
# 1. Create a free account at https://clerk.com
# 2. Create a new application
# 3. Copy your publishable key from the Clerk Dashboard → API Keys
# 4. Rename this file to .env.local and paste your key below
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_replace_with_your_key_here

# Optionally enable specific sign-in methods via the Clerk Dashboard (Email, Google, GitHub, etc.)
